"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-cycling-katie-archibald-injury-garden-olympics-paris-2024-b2565965.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The 30-year-old Scot broke her tibia and fibula and dislocated an ankle  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Two-timeOlympicchampion cyclistKatie Archibaldwill missParis 2024after suffering a double leg break in a freak garden accident.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old Scotfractured a tibia and fibula and dislocated an ankle having tripped over a step in her backyard.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also sustained substantial ligament damage during the incident on Tuesday and has since undergone surgery.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I tripped over a step in the garden and managed to, somehow, dislocate my ankle; break my tibia and fibula; and rip two ligaments off the bone.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What the heck,\\\" wrote Archibaldon social media.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was on Tuesday, and since then I have been in full princess mode (assuming it took a full team of A&E doctors and nurses to get Cinderella's foot back in line with the slipper \\ud83d\\udc4d).\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1075, \"end\": 1078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emergency_department\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.377033004845808e-33, \"text\": \"A&E\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emergency_department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emergency_department\"}, {\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinderella\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8844026109583675e-34, \"text\": \"Cinderella\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinderella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinderella\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Had surgery yesterday to pin the bones back together and reattach the ligaments.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then hopefully this afternoon I will be going home.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A hundred apologies for what this means for the Olympic team, which I have been told will not involve me.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am still processing that bit of news, but thought I better confirm it publicly instead of leaving it to the grapevine (trip hazard and all that).\\\"\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics take place between 26 July and 11 August butnow will not involve Archibald, who won team pursuit gold at Rio 2016 and thentopped the podium in the madisonalongside Laura Kenny at Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1633, \"end\": 1642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\", \"score\": 0.9032158340345134, \"rank\": 0.10715508096240656, \"text\": \"Archibald\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\"}, {\"begin\": 1732, \"end\": 1743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Kenny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\"}, {\"begin\": 1747, \"end\": 1752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9916471604907015, \"rank\": 0.008422005929323254, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The likeable Brit has endured a tough couple of years since Tokyo,missing the 2022 Commonwealth Gamesin Birmingham after colliding with a vehicle amid a series of injury setbacks, while later that summer, her partner - 37-year-old mountain biker Rab Wardell - died suddenly in bed beside her.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1820, \"end\": 1825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9916471604907015, \"rank\": 0.008422005929323254, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2006, \"end\": 2009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abba_Arikha\", \"score\": 0.992990047468165, \"rank\": 0.00705876048690213, \"text\": \"Rab\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abba_Arikha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abba_Arikha\"}, {\"begin\": 2010, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wardell,_New_South_Wales\", \"score\": 0.5124502886127023, \"rank\": 0.6250000000000604, \"text\": \"Wardell\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wardell,_New_South_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wardell,_New_South_Wales\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wardell suffered a cardiac arrestin his sleep just two days after taking victory at the Scottish MTB XC Championships and Archibaldrevealed how she \\\"tried and tried\\\"to resuscitate him  \\\"I think you have heard that Rab died yesterday morning,\\\" she tweeted at the time.\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"score\": 0.9888923391261779, \"rank\": 0.011229601745339168, \"text\": \"Scottish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still do not understand what's happened; if this is real; why he'd be taken now - so healthy and happy.\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He went into cardiac arrest while we were lying in bed.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried and tried, and the paramedics arrived within minutes but his heart stopped and they could not bring him back.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mine stopped with it.\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love him so much and need him here with me.\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I need him here so badly, but he's gone.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not describe this pain.\\\"\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In her Instagram post after this week's surgery, Archibald paid tribute to the medical team that operated on her.\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2753, \"end\": 2762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.971630620839928e-24, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 2795, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\", \"score\": 0.9032158340345134, \"rank\": 0.10715508096240656, \"text\": \"Archibald\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A hundred thank yous for the fabulous doctors, nurses, radiographers, porters, physios, surgeons and more at the Manchester Royal Infirmary,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 3013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Might be back with more updates, might be gone from the socials for a bit - TBC.\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3095, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ciao for now.\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Katie x\\\".\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additional reporting by PA  Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3201, \"end\": 3212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.238093474149657e-16, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"